This paper is primarily focused on person re-identification, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning networks, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of a clustering task, which could fall under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also introduces a new loss function, which could fall under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the model, which could fall under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
